Package sportstournament.main

Class Club

java.lang.Object
sportstournament.main.Team
sportstournament.main.Club
public class Club extends Team
This class implements a club which is a subclass of Team. The club contains methods which affect the active team, the reserves and the inventory.
Author:
Reuben Schoonbee and Isaac Steele
